{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-note-template-tsx","path":"/elixir/tasks","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<ul>\n<li>build on top of the spawn functions to provide better error reports and introspection</li>\n<li>abstraction for running code concurrently</li>\n<li>useful for running single async functions</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"taskstart1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#taskstart1\" aria-label=\"taskstart1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Task.start/1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>does not return the result</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"elixir\"><pre class=\"language-elixir\"><code class=\"language-elixir\">Task<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>start<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">fn</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-></span> IO<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>puts<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Async code\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">end</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"taskasync1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#taskasync1\" aria-label=\"taskasync1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Task.async/1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>returns Task struct containing the result and other information like owner and pid</li>\n<li>to get the result you need to use <code class=\"language-text\">Task.yield/1</code> or <code class=\"language-text\">Task.await/1</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"taskyield1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#taskyield1\" aria-label=\"taskyield1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Task.yield/1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>does not raise an exception</li>\n<li>returns nil when task is not yet completed</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"taskshutdown1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#taskshutdown1\" aria-label=\"taskshutdown1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Task.shutdown/1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>stops a task</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"taskasync_stream3\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#taskasync_stream3\" aria-label=\"taskasync_stream3 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Task.async_stream/3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>returns a stream</li>\n<li>works like <code class=\"language-text\">Enum.map/2</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">Task.async/2</code> combined</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"tasksupervisor\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tasksupervisor\" aria-label=\"tasksupervisor permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Task.Supervisor</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>built-in supervisor for Task</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"date":"March 07, 2021","path":"/elixir/tasks","title":"Tasks","category":"Elixir"}}},"pageContext":{}}}